{"tid":1047398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳《人民日報》前主任 因「抑鬱症」墜樓身亡","createTime":"2019-03-05T02:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T02:43:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2fccf9b4e53e80527c496fe777fe73799d6e72c7","tid":1047398,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190304/large/1551711772_c5b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190304%2Flarge%2F1551711772_c5b2.jpg&h=cbc01e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地熱傳中共黨媒《人民日報》員工的微信截圖，截圖顯示有人指今日中午收到《人民日報》研究部前主任劉學淵因抑鬱症墮樓身亡的消息，同時還配了2張照片。該員工寫道，「中午驚聞噩耗，雖然逝者與我沒有交集，但畢竟曾在一個大院共事十多年，不禁心有戚戚焉。願人類早日戰勝抑鬱症。」<br />\n<br />\n去年11月，《人民日報》旗下雜誌《新聞戰線》總編輯胡欣，也因抑鬱症墮樓身亡。 <br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線：<br />\n珍愛生命長者熱線:2382 0881<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線:2389 2222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言):2896 0000<br />\n生命熱線:2382 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線:18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線:2343 2255 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190304/59330524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59330524&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcakx5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=29975f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59330524&h=e2cc9098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190304/59330524</a>"},{"pid":"f686812c48998131974cd6fed505ddeefd3e8505","tid":1047398,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:20:22.000Z","msg":"可以去見毛主席了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f989d6037c1fb548201b8a90cd9ba5338836e729","tid":1047398,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"《大時代》cap圖"},{"pid":"94f5b8